"x offset\n"
": Pixel-independent offset relative to the choice of alignment on the x-axis.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/watermark.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"y offset\n"
": Pixel-independent offset relative to the choice of alignment on the y-axis.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
