#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/lighttable/styles.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "Styles can either be created within this panel or in the [history stack](../darkroom/history-stack.md) module in the darkroom.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/lighttable/styles.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid "A list of all available styles is displayed in the module. A search field above the list allows you to locate a style by name or description. This module also allows styles to be edited and deleted.\n"
