#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/tagging.md
#, markdown-text, no-wrap
msgid ""
"![list-tree-icon](./tagging/list-tree-icon.png#icon) list/tree\n"
": Toggle the display of tags between the straight _list_ view and hierarchical _tree_ view.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
